{"tid":735934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得啲人要借錢結婚好仆街呀？","createTime":"2018-07-10T01:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T01:44:28.000Z","uid":64961,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04e5e72115f95906a135a679882bf58e224cadbe","tid":735934,"uid":64961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的 琴日男朋友同我講佢個fd結婚有啲數目上嘅問題突然間有筆數要俾 要問佢幾萬蚊借住先 一星期後還<br />\n我心諗 酒都未擺都係俾住訂先㗎姐 有幾大筆數要問人借呀？ 咁大個人仲要結得婚幾萬蚊會唔會拎唔到呀？<br />\n幾萬都無就咪撚結啦 有邊個結婚唔洗用錢呀？個個都借咪好唔撚得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有如果一星期就還到嘅錢又洗唔洗問人借呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明唔方咁快會還 甚至唔撚還啦<br />\n男朋友仲信曬個fd 一放工就過數俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cab429264d4a3e6288df9d6956539ef21aa988","tid":735934,"uid":82450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"分手 唔好再對住個豬閪男友"},{"pid":"b015c0a3d034dcbc997ec6f541818c4a10352ea8","tid":735934,"uid":116688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:27:12.000Z","msg":"預咗收唔返㗎喎"},{"pid":"ec28334b6bd886a103aeb121cc3fff5b136377b3","tid":735934,"uid":189053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9baffa235fce3cdb09e4e78a1ad8845de350c68a","tid":735934,"uid":10453,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"講到一星期咁快還到，分明搵水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391c532ef1865f171e3a73ae55db9c21b5571e7a","tid":735934,"uid":193957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"以前買樓買車都係一炮俾，而家都有得供，遲下連擺酒結婚都做分期咯！"},{"pid":"ffb5f6d53844005c479ccdd1a9765344169a55f1","tid":735934,"uid":64961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit